text:
Luca, good job on the shoot.
I think it turned out really well.

Despite the time constraints,
You managed to prepare thoroughly──
Can't you be quiet for a bit...

Producer-san, great job to you too.
Thanks to you, it was a really good shoot.

She has a good understanding of the image, And in addition
to our requests, she also brings out her own personality.

She has presence as well,
Her talent is quite remarkable......

Thank you very much
I'm glad you're praising Ikaruga's talent......!
